

=Bio=

"Hannah Stewart is a Research Associate at the Royal College of Art and an independent researcher. Alongside Andrew Sleigh she was commissioned to produce the UK Makerspaces Open Dataset for NESTA. 

Her Phd research with the Creative Exchange focused on the values and practices of the makermovement, indieweb and open data communities.

Hannah does curiosity driven research and making to explore what futures are possible or probable; using artifacts, speculative design and action research projects to establish factors of influence and trends."


